<p>Make a ranged spell attack against a <a href="/wiki/Creature" title="Creature">creature</a> you can see. On a hit, the target takes 4d6 <a href="/wiki/Damage_Type#Radiant" title="Damage Type">radiant</a> damage, and before the end of your next turn, the next attack roll made on it has <a href="/wiki/How_to_Play#Advantage_and_Disadvantage" title="How to Play">advantage</a>.
</p><p><b>At Higher Levels:</b> The damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 1st.
</p>
